title: Euro 2016 Qualifier Highlights - 5th September 2015 - hdtv x264

SPORT: Euro 2016 Qualifier Highlights
On: itv HD  
Date: Saturday 5th September 2015 
Time: 22:45 to 00:15 

Jacqui Oatley is joined by Robbie Fowler for highlights of the week's Euro 2016 qualifying matches as all four home nations and the Republic of Ireland aim to reach the finals in France next summer. England, Northern Ireland and the Republic all start as heavy favourites on the road against San Marino, the Faroe Islands and Gibraltar respectively, while Wales face a tougher test in Cyprus and Scotland travel to Georgia hoping to keep the pressure on in Group D. Commentary comes from Clive Tyldesley, Sam Matterface, Joe Speight, Derek Rae and David Stowell.
